Package edu.missouri.drone.static_height

Class HuangDrone

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mmkrusniak.drone.Drone
      • com.mmkrusniak.drone.static_height.OfflineDrone
        • com.mmkrusniak.drone.static_height.JiaoDrone
          • com.mmkrusniak.drone.static_height.CombinatoryJiaoDrone
            • com.mmkrusniak.drone.static_height.HuangDrone
  • public class HuangDrone
extends CombinatoryJiaoDrone
    An offline drone which splits complex polygons into simpler ones by splitting concave vertices using Huang's cellular decomposition. It is similar to Jiao's but somewhat more thorough (it is exponentially recursive rather than polynomial). It performs well but the decomposition is very time-intensive.
